===Etymology===
From {{term|rêver||to dream|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|frm|fr}} {{term|resver||to wander, be lost in vague thoughts, induce in error|lang=frm}}, from {{etyl|fro|fr}} {{term|resver||to consider, reflect, be delirious|lang=fro}}, probably of {{etyl|gem|fr}} origin, from {{etyl|frk|fr}} *{{term||raswjan, rāswan, rēswan|to consider, conjecture|lang=frk}} from {{proto|Germanic|ræsi-, rǣsw-|to think, suppose, consider|lang=fr}} from {{proto|Indo-European|rei-|to reason, count|lang=fr}}. Akin to {{etyl|ang|-}} {{term|ræswan|rǣswan|to think, consider, suspect, conjecture|lang=ang}}.

